elements.name: To verify whether user is able to select Customer Admin in User Category for creating user.

steps.name: Click on Customer Host ID Act Link
Enter CIF number "118624" in Host Customer Id TextField
click on Account Selection Act Link
Click on Parameters Setting Act Link
Click on user level act link
Enter value in Upper Limit TextField "1000"
Enter value in per Day Limit TextField "1000"
Enter value in Future Transaction Limit TextField "1000"
Click on user level act link
Enter value in lower Limit Textfield "5"
Enter value in Upper Limit Textfield "100"
Enter value in per Day Limit TextField "100"
Enter value in Future Transaction Limit TextField "100"
Click on authorization matrix act link
Select value in Transaction dropdown "All Financial"
Enter value in Minimum transaction amount Textfield "5"
Enter value in Maximum transaction amount Textfield "100"
Select value in Repeat Flag DropDown "No"
select USER option "CUSTOMER ADMIN" and added to right side
Click on single move right button
click on Pool radio button and enter remark "okay"
enter the reference number and click on search button
click on approve radio button and enter remark "okay"
fetch pop-up box text click on ok button
Click on Customer User Administration Icon
Select "CUSTOMER ADMIN" value in User Category DropDown
click on Pool radio button and enter remark "okay"
enter the reference number and click on search button
click on approve radio button and enter remark "okay"
fetch pop-up box text click on ok button
Click on Customer User Administration Icon
Select "CUSTOMER ADMIN" value in User Category DropDown
click on Pool radio button and enter remark "okay"
enter the reference number and click on search button
click on approve radio button and enter remark "okay"
fetch pop-up box text click on ok button

name: select Customer Admin in User Category
